  text-align:center;
  color:#fff;
  margin:18px 0 10px;

  opacity:0.9;
}

  list-style:none;
  padding:0;
  margin-top:10px;
}

.sidebar ul li a {
  display:block;
  padding:12px 22px;
  color:#cfe6ff;
  text-decoration:none;
  font-size:15px;
  border-left:4px solid transparent;
  transition:0.25s;
}

.sidebar ul li a:hover {
  background:#1e4057;
  border-left-color:#42c9ff;
  color:#fff;
}

/* ----- CONTEÚDO PRINCIPAL ----- */

  width:100%;
  margin-left:280px;
  padding:40px 70px;
}

/* Seções premium */
.section {
  background:#fff;
  border-radius:14px;
  padding:40px;

}

.section h1 {
  font-size:26px;
  color:#1a3a52;
  font-weight:700;
  margin-bottom:14px;
  padding-bottom:10px;
  border-bottom:3px solid #42c9ff;

.section h2, .section h3 {
  margin-top:22px;
  color:#2c5aa0;
  font-weight:600;
  font-size:19px;
}

/* ----- Formulário Premium ----- */
.form-grid {
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
  gap:22px;
  margin-top:20px;
}

.form-group {
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
}

.form-group label {
  font-weight:600;
  margin-bottom:6px;
  color:#1a3a52;
}

.form-group input, textarea {
  padding:12px;
  border-radius:8px;
  font-size:15px;
  border:2px solid #dce3eb;
  transition:0.25s;
}

.form-group input:focus, textarea:focus {
  border-color:#42c9ff;
  box-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(0,174,255,0.22);
  outline:none;
}

textarea {
  min-height:140px;
  resize:vertical;
}

/* ----- Imagens Premium ----- */
.image-box {
  width:100%;
  min-height:260px;
  border:2px dashed #cfd9e2;
  border-radius:12px;
  display:flex;
  justify-content:center;
  align-items:center;
  overflow:hidden;
  background:#f9fafc;
  margin-top:20px;
}

.image-box.empty {
  color:#888;
  font-size:16px;
}

.image-box img {
  width:100%;
  height:100%;
  object-fit:contain;
}

/* ----- TABELAS PREMIUM ----- */
.table-wrap {
  width:100%;
  overflow-x:auto;
  margin-top:20px;
}

table {
  width:100%;
  border-collapse:collapse;
  background:#fff;
  border-radius:10px;
  overflow:hidden;
}

table th {
  background:#eef3f7;
  padding:14px;
  font-size:14px;
  color:#333;
  border-bottom:2px solid #dce3eb;
}

table td {

}

table tr:hover td {
  background:#1a3a52;
  color:white;
}

table input {
  width:100%;
  padding:10px;
  border-radius:6px;
  border:1px solid #d1d9e2;
}

.btn-add {
  margin-top:14px;
  background:#42c9ff;
  padding:12px 26px;
  border:none;
  color:#fff;
  border-radius:8px;
  font-size:15px;
  cursor:pointer;
  transition:0.25s;
}

.btn-add:hover {
  background:#1ea7d4;
}

.btn-delete {
  background:none;
  border:none;
  font-size:20px;
  cursor:pointer;
  color:#d9534f;
}

}

<script>
/* Mobile sidebar open/close — mantém o menu fechado por padrão e evita "colado" */
(function () {
  const menuToggle = document.getElementById('menuToggle');
  const overlay = document.getElementById('mobileOverlay');

  if (!menuToggle || !overlay) return;

  function isMobile() {
    return window.innerWidth <= 900;
  }

  function openMenu() {
    document.body.classList.add('sidebar-open');
    menuToggle.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'true');
    overlay.setAttribute('aria-hidden', 'false');
  }
  function closeMenu() {
    document.body.classList.remove('sidebar-open');
    menuToggle.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');
    overlay.setAttribute('aria-hidden', 'true');
  }
  function toggleMenu() {
    if (document.body.classList.contains('sidebar-open')) closeMenu();
    else openMenu();
  }

  menuToggle.addEventListener('click', toggleMenu);
  overlay.addEventListener('click', closeMenu);

  // controla visibilidade do botão no carregamento e resize
  function updateToggle() {
    if (isMobile()) {
      menuToggle.style.display = 'block';
      // garante que o menu comece fechado no mobile
      closeMenu();
    } else {
      menuToggle.style.display = 'none';
      closeMenu();
    }
  }

  window.addEventListener('resize', updateToggle);
  updateToggle();
})();
</script>
